data.description: PRIVACY, PRIVACY, PRIVACY! Located on almost 5 wooded acres, through a beautifully canopied driveway, this gorgeous, updated home is a must see! The sellers have recently renovated the kitchen to include a LARGE island with an oversized farmstyle sink, new appliances, luxury vinyl plank flooring, granite countertops and updated lighting in the main part of the home. There is a new vanity, countertop and toilet in the second bathroom, NEW roof and NEW HVAC system (both installed July 2023), NEW pool pump motor (June 2023), newer shed (2021), newer water softener (2021), and hurricane shutters! The interior was just painted, including the ceilings. All of this and a large pool with screened patio that is perfect for entertaining all of your guests! This one is a MUST SEE!
